childrenXml:
<IncludeJavascriptFiles>
    <File><![CDATA[/MSP/external/resources/js/budgetPlanning.js]]></File>
</IncludeJavascriptFiles>
<PreRenderServerScript>
<![CDATA[

if (!tbl.id > 0) {
	var withBusinessCase = $request.getParameter("WITH_BUSINESS_CASE");
	if (withBusinessCase){
		var goalAlignmentParameters = {"cse_planGoal": false, "cse_percentCostAllocation": false, "cse_value": false, "cse_description": true};
		var budgetAlignmentParameters = {"cse_budgetType": false, "cse_percentCostAllocation": false, "cse_description": true};
		var FTEsandCostsEstimationParameters = {"cse_type": false, "cse_organizationUnit": false, "cse_description": true, "cse_Q1Cost": false, "cse_Q2Cost": false, "cse_Q3Cost": false,
		"cse_Q4Cost": false, "cse_totalCost": false, "cse_Q1FTEs": false,
		"cse_Q2FTEs": false, "cse_Q3FTEs": false, "cse_Q4FTEs": false,
		"cse_totalFTEs": false, "cse_remainingCost": false, "cse_remainingCostDuringBudgetCutover": false,
		"cse_actualCost": false, "cse_actualCostonCurrentBudget": false, "cse_remainingFTEs": false,
		"cse_remainingFTEsDuringBudgetCutover": false, "cse_actualFTEs": false, "cse_actualFTEsonCurrentBudget": false};

		Project.populateTable('cse_currentBudgetSource', 'cse_goalAlignment', 'cse_goalAlignment', 'com.msp.dao.entities.cse.custom.Cse_GoalAlignment', goalAlignmentParameters);
		Project.populateTable('cse_currentBudgetSource', 'cse_budgetAlignment', 'cse_budgetAlignment', 'com.msp.dao.entities.cse.custom.Cse_BudgetAlignment', budgetAlignmentParameters);
		Project.populateTable('cse_currentBudgetSource', 'cse_FTEsandCostsEstimation', 'cse_FTEsandCostsEstimation', 'com.msp.dao.entities.cse.custom.Cse_HighLevelEstimation', FTEsandCostsEstimationParameters);
		
		var additionalFieldsParameters = {"cse_businessJustification": true, "cse_actionPlanSummary": true, "cse_alternativesSummary": true, "cse_risksSummary": true};
		Project.updateAdditionalFields('cse_currentBudgetSource',additionalFieldsParameters, "com.msp.dao.entities.cse.custom.Cse_DemandActivity");
	}
}
]]>
</PreRenderServerScript>
